		"name": "12",
		"description": "In a dark cave, waves lap softly in the distance as Yvette’s cracked helmet glows faintly. She struggles to stand, but upon removing her helmet, she finds she can breathe. The cave slowly illuminates, revealing a breathtaking arctic ice cavern with an endless ocean. A voice, 'Ocean,' speaks to her, acknowledging her thoughts and trusting her. Yvette’s skin glows bioluminescent as she kneels to scoop water into a test tube. But as she catches her reflection, she sees herself holding money and shaking hands with global leaders, a cold look in her eyes. Startled, she falls back, breaking the test tube.",
